  B4 -->|proxies to TMDB| C1
  B6 -->|auth operations| C3
  B8 -->|watchlist CRUD| C3

  B3 -->|returns reply + recommendations| A3
  B4 -->|returns search/results| A2
  B8 -->|returns watchlist data| A2

